Subject: The Future of Virtual Reality
Description: With the Oculus Rift being bought by media giant Facebook, the cautionary tales of science fiction seem closer than ever to reality.  Join authors Ernie Cline and John Scalzi, and Android VR creator Gameface Labs, as they talk about where our communal virtual fantasy is headed.
